The committee shall consist of the following representatives, one (1) of whom shall be male, and one (1) of whom shall be female, except in paragraphs (f) and (i):
Two (2) coaches, who may be active or former coaches;
Two (2) current superintendents of school districts that have high school athletic programs;
Two (2) current high school principals;
Two (2) former players, who participated in at least one (1) state tournament;
Two (2) athletic directors, active or former;
Two (2) former members of the board of control of the high school athletic association designated by the state board to govern interscholastic athletics;
Two (2) active referees;
Two (2) citizen members; and
Two (2) members of the General Assembly, one (1) appointed by the Senate President and one (1) appointed by the Speaker of the House.
